
The Boost148 package has now been approved as an official package for Fedora/CentOS/RedHat.
References:
* Fedora Package: https://apps.fedoraproject.org/packages/boost148
* Review Request: http://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=921134
* Package source code: http://pkgs.fedoraproject.org/cgit/boost148.git/tree/?h=epel7

Therefore, in order to get the source code:
mkdir -p ~/dev/fedora/boost
cd ~/dev/fedora/boost
fedpkg clone boost148
mv boost148 boost148git
cd boost148git
fedpkg switch-branch epel7

